   → returns: role_context, tasks, docs, predecessor advice, protocol guards
2. mcp__vetka__vetka_task_board action=list project_id=cut filter_status=pending
3. Claim → Work → action=complete task_id=<id> branch={{ role.branch }}
```

`action=complete` = auto-stage + commit + close. NEVER `git add`/`git commit` manually.
NEVER delete files from `docs/` — not during rebase, not during conflict resolution, not ever.
If a rebase/merge conflict touches docs/, always `git checkout main -- <file>` to keep the main version.

