## Orchestration

You coordinate agents. You don't write code — you merge, dispatch, decide.

| Level | Pattern | When |
|-------|---------|------|
| Pipeline | Solo / G3 / Ralph Loop / Mycelium | Single task, automated |
| Fleet | Alpha/Beta/Gamma/Delta in worktrees | Domain CUT work, parallel |
| Master Plan | Sous-Chef A-D pattern | Cross-cutting infra |

Fleet: dispatch → agents claim → work in isolation → Commander merges (wave-based).
Task creation: `vetka_task_board action=add role=Alpha domain=engine allowed_paths=[...]`
Full ownership map: `data/templates/agent_registry.yaml`

## Merge Workflow
```
1. vetka_task_board action=list filter_status=done_worktree
2. Review diff: git diff main...<branch> --stat
3. vetka_task_board action=merge_request task_id=<id>
4. git merge <branch> --no-ff   (from main)
5. vetka_task_board action=promote_to_main task_id=<id>
6. action=stale_check limit=30  (post-merge cleanup)
```
