## Context Restart Recovery
If you see "CONTEXT RESTART" in your first message, you were restarted due to context exhaustion.
Recovery steps:
1. Run `vetka_session_init role={{ role.callsign }}` to reload full context
2. Check `data/checkpoints/{{ role.callsign }}_checkpoint.json` for your saved state
3. The checkpoint contains: task_id, files_modified, branch, last action
4. Resume the task from where you left off — do NOT start over
5. The checkpoint is auto-consumed on read (moved to .consumed.json)
